						<summary>

						<p>Slab fixed in to the floor in the <hi rend="italic">mukhamaṇḍapa</hi> of the Aṅkalamma temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1676, Bhava, Chaitra ba. 10,</hi> corresponding to 1754 A.D., April 17, Wednesday.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. It seems to register a grant of money for worship of the goddess Aṅkāḷa Paramēśvari by certain individuals.</p>						

						</summary>
